The Samsung 971p is adjusted for X11.  Perfectly.  In console it is off
by a few pixels (left-shifted).  Can we alter any console settings to
fix this problem?  I assume we want to leave the DDC settings alone
since X11 works fine.  For X11 we use nvidia drivers, and in console
vesafb + fbcon with the same 1280x1024 resolution.  Console border is
shifted by a letter or two, so reading is hard.

M.


